| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0775 — Recovery Inhibition (ALP-001)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: c8497012-c919-5ccc-9ff1-e4ff2a005d1a"
